reviewText: I originally got this primarily for Working Girl (OMG that song just randomly starts playing in my head and then I have to watch the movie!), but I really enjoyed The Devil Wears Prada, as well. I'm sure Picture Perfect would be a lot of fun if I could get past the repulsive moral sea it's buried under, but I'm odd that way.
Head Over Heels is a spoof that is great fun.  Devil Wears Prada contains wonderful acting and a marvelous message. Well worth the time and money.
